    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ついに撮影の日がやってきたわね\nま、私にとっては朝ごはん前ですけど？",
      "startTime": 5.9000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "無理のないように頑張るんだぞ\nあれだけ練習したんだ、千紗ならきっと大丈夫だ！",
      "startTime": 12.6666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふん。誰に対して言っているのかしら？　偉そうに\nあなたは私の演技を黙って見ていればいいのよ！",
      "startTime": 21.7000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "悪い子というよりもツンデレみたいになってないか？\nそういう方向性も悪くないかもしれないが……",
      "startTime": 30.3666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ツ、ツンデレなんかじゃないです！　あ、こほん！\n誰がツンデレよ。デタラメ言わないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 38.4000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ撮影に行ってくるわ\nお前はそこで黙って見ていることね",
      "startTime": 45.1000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。ここで応援しておくとするよ\n初の大舞台、後悔のないようにな！",
      "startTime": 52.0333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、何よその顔。私のせいと言いたいの？\nあなたが勝手に転んだだけじゃない",
      "startTime": 63.2666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "そうやってすぐ私のせいにしようとして……\nあなたって本当に性格が悪いのねぇ？",
      "startTime": 70.6000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（普段の穏やかな千紗らしくない、完璧なまでに）\n（性格の悪い言動の数々……いい調子だ）",
      "startTime": 78.4333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季から聞いた話だと、千紗は寮に戻ってからも）\n（ずっとあのキャラを演じていたらしい）",
      "startTime": 86.4333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（今の千紗ならどんな状況であろうとも）\n（役を最後まで演じ切れるはずだ！）",
      "startTime": 92.1666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……あなたはいつもそうよね\n周りを見ずに自分のことばっかり",
      "startTime": 99.1000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "私、そういう一直線な子って大嫌いなの\nどうして旦那様はこんなやつのこと……っ",
      "startTime": 107.0333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（監督さんも千紗の演技を見て驚いているな）\n（まさかの出来に舌を巻いているんだろう）",
      "startTime": 113.4666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "何？　その顔。私に文句でもあるのかしら？\nあなたって本当に――カット、ですって？",
      "startTime": 121.0000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私の演技のどこに問題があったというの？\nなるほど……もっと相手を睨むように、ね",
      "startTime": 130.5333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ。あなたがそれを望むなら\nそういう風に演じてあげる",
      "startTime": 139.1000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私に偉そうな指示をしたこと……\nいつか後悔させてあげるわ！",
      "startTime": 145.5666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……むしろ役が抜けていない）\n（とりあえず後で監督やスタッフさん達に謝っておこう）",
      "startTime": 151.3000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "何？　その顔。私に文句でもあるのかしら？\nあなたって本当に……気に食わないわね",
      "startTime": 160.6000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私はね、あなたをここから追い出すためなら\nどんな手段も、いとわないつもりよ？",
      "startTime": 168.8000000914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "悔しかったら、私にやり返してみせなさいよ\nまぁ？　お優しいあなたには無理でしょうけどね？",
      "startTime": 175.6666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影後",
      "startTime": 180.7801323769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}。撮影終わらせてきてやったわよ\n労いの言葉を掛ける権利を与えてあげるわ",
      "startTime": 186.9666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、千紗。でも、撮影は終わったんだから\nもういつもの千紗に戻ってもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 194.7666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "あら、そう？　なら……ふぅ。お疲れ様です\nなんだか、久しぶりに普通に話す気がします",
      "startTime": 205.3333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっとやり過ぎちゃったでしょうか？\nスタッフさんにも酷いこと言っちゃって……",
      "startTime": 213.7666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが私のかわりに\n先に謝っておいてくれたんですよね？",
      "startTime": 220.6333334248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narucorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。でも、すみれはもちろん、監督も演者さん達も\n怒ってなくて、むしろ新感覚だと好評だったぞ",
      "startTime": 228.000002126,
      "sfxList": []
